"""User

* `id
* `username`
* `email`
* `password_hash`
* `role` (`buyer`, `seller`, `admin`)
* `created_at`

---

Auction

* `id`
* `title`
* `description`
* `starting_price`
* `current_price`
* `image_url`
* `status` (`active`, `closed`, `cancelled`)
* `end_time`
* `seller_id` (FK → User.id)
* `winner_id` (FK → User.id, nullable)


Bid

* `id`
* `amount`
* `timestamp`
* `bidder_id` (FK → User.id)
* `auction_id` (FK → Auction.id)
"""